text: U.S. Route 18 (US 18) is an east-west United States highway in the Midwestern United States. The west end is at Interstate 25, US 20, US 26, and US 87 in Orin, Wyoming. Its east end is at Lincoln Memorial Drive in downtown Milwaukee, Wisconsin. The highway is long. ==References== Category:U.S. Highways
title: U.S. Route 18
